Chino Corporation Logo Chino Corporation is a Japanese manufacturer of measuring instruments and controllers. Working as a Japan Calibration Service System-certified supplier, it manufactures and supplies a wide range of electrical measuring equipment, controllers, and systems. Chino also manufactures and supplies calibration systems and conducts traceability tests, and has been certified by the National Institute of Technology and Evaluation as a calibration accreditation company. Source
